{"tid":1339734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制元朗區行動","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:16:58.000Z","uid":154617,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d256dd3ec027fde09dcc8dfab4ba61d19249494","tid":1339734,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"太嬲，第一次出post<br />\n如果1919請見諒<br />\n<br />\n元朗鄉黑既行為簡直無法無天<br />\n非法行為包括<br />\n1）自稱三合會成員<br />\n2）非法集結<br />\n3）暴動<br />\n4）傷人<br />\n等等等等<br />\n<br />\n香港市民對此予以最高譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起光復元朗，我覺得抵制元朗區會比較好<br />\n硬碰硬一定無著數<br />\n鄉黑又唔怕比黑警拉<br />\n比人打死都係賤命一條，無野輸<br />\n我地應該要留返咁多位義士既體力<br />\n用抵制黎減低鄉黑勢力<br />\n<br />\n抵制行動大家可以傾傾，初步諗到少少idea<br />\n1）呼籲同宣傳香港各大市民避免前往元朗區。大量黑社會人士住係元朗區，大家都唔想無啦啦比人扑濕嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）元朗區朋友麻煩報料邊d鋪係鄉黑經營，各位市民食飯買野都唔想有生命威脅嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要目的係打擊區內（主要係鄉黑）既收入來源<br />\n黑社會都係利字當頭<br />\n手停口停我睇下佢地仲會唔會咁撚惡<br />\n<br />\n有無元朗巴絲比下意見，呢個方向正唔正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f767a5c9d5e940c73cdd9fb53e0057798b89792e","tid":1339734,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"咁d居民咪好慘"},{"pid":"44de7fc69d19d5d47779d8c47f2de65d199b9eee","tid":1339734,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f767a5c9d5e940c73cdd9fb53e0057798b89792e","tid":1339734,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"咁d居民咪好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"大家集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過比市民認清邊d係黑社會經營既咪仲好，其他鋪同居民應該好歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c76220f05d57a0dab442e00cdf49f01f3e3fb9","tid":1339734,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9f10f10482408aaa0b938107b186af5419f99de","tid":1339734,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20aa4bf027e1092e2ab4989ad727d187d591dc49","tid":1339734,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f10f10482408aaa0b938107b186af5419f99de","tid":1339734,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"先撩者賤"},{"pid":"c387c8047dbdb7ea24a5a240c176c519db03fd6c","tid":1339734,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7557c778843e00395e67b9ee44b1ba800223fc2","tid":1339734,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}